labels","id":1254989,"node_id":"MDk6TWlsZXN0b25lMTI1NDk4OQ==","number":6,"title":"3.0.1","description":"","creator":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":76,"state":"closed","created_at":"2015-08-14T10:53:58Z","updated_at":"2015-08-14T12:30:22Z","due_on":"2015-08-06T07:00:00Z","closed_at":"2015-08-14T11:12:27Z"},"comments":0,"created_at":"2015-07-31T10:41:42Z","updated_at":"2015-08-14T11:10:56Z","closed_at":"2015-07-31T10:49:15Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When query builder cache is enabled, (`$this->db->start_cache()` [Documentation](http://www.codeigniter.com/user_guide/database/query_builder.html#query-builder-caching)) any data added via `$this->db->where_in()` does not take into account any saved cache.\n\nI believe I have tracked this down to [here](https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/blob/develop/system/database/DB_query_builder.php#L810) in the DB_query_builder class.\n\nShould this be \n\n`$prefix = (count($this->qb_where) === 0`**`&& count($this->qb_cache_where) == 0`**`) ? $this->_group_get_type('') : $this->_group_get_type($type);`\n\ninstead of\n\n`$prefix = (count($this->qb_where) === 0) ? $this->_group_get_type('') : $this->_group_get_type($type);`\n\nThis issue only appears when adding `$this->db->where_in()` after a query has been ran.\nExample\n\n``` $this->db->start_cache();\n$this->db->where('my_field', 'my_val');\n$query = $this->db->get('my_table'); // Works \n$this->db->where_in('my_new_field', array('1','2','3'));\n$query2 = $this->db->get('my_table'); // Fails\n$this->db->stop_cache()\n```\n\nThe documentation does not state that the where_in can can cached (only select, from, join, where, like, group_by, having, order_by, set). However the code in the DB_query_builder class adds the query into the cache [see here](https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/blob/develop/system/database/DB_query_builder.php#L817) if it's enabled.\n","closed_by":{"login":"narfbg","id":1058011,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEwNTgwMTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1058011?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg","html_url":"https://github.com/narfbg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/narfbg/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issue